+  // Return the task's windowless Browser on `profile`, creating it on first use.
+  // If a Browser already exists for the task but on a DIFFERENT profile (the
+  // task switched identities), the old one is closed and a new one is made.
+  Browser* GetOrCreateTaskBrowser(const std::string& task_id, Profile* profile);
+
+  // Resolve a `profile_key` to a `Profile` and run `cb` (null on failure).
+  // Empty key → the shell's default profile (synchronous). A pooled key →
+  // get-or-create the `slayzone-<key>` profile (async on first use) + hold a
